### Example

```csharp
using Starcounter;
using System;

class Program {
    static void Main(string[] args) {
        // Foo can not be successfully invoked if PreFoo() is not
        // invoked previously. If Foo() is called like this, it will
        // generate an error 4216.
        Db.Foo();
    }
```

### Resolution
_There is currently no code example available on how to remedy error 4216. Please modify the code below in a way that can describe how to remedy this error._

```csharp
using Starcounter;
using System;

class Program {
    static void Main(string[] args) {
        // We call PreFoo() prior to calling Foo(). Now, we will
        // no longer experience error 4216.
        Db.PreFoo();
        Db.Foo();
    }
}
```
